title: Yosuga no Sora Partial Patch (Sora & Kazuha)
description:
Yosuga no Sora Partial Patch (Sora & Kazuha)
Company: Sphere
Release date: Dec 05, 2008
Genre: Visual Novel
Language: English Subtitled


Summary: Partial Patch Only!
Translates Kazuha route and Sora route only. All other routes untranslated. 
Kazuha route is fully edited but Sora route is unedited. That means if you play Sora now you will be playing "raw translations". The sentences won't grammar well and they won't flow well. 


Translators: vvav, Koto, bekyuubi, Xilexio, trjr, Joyjason, Zky, Cafe, deltakei, valerauko
Proofreading: linktriforce007
For More info visit: http://trjr.wordpress.com
